			<title>巴西三軍司令同日集體辭職，引發國內政治地震</title>
			<link>https%3A%2F%2Finternationalnewsstation.tw%2Fpost7744%7D%2F%E5%B7%B4%E8%A5%BF%E4%B8%89%E8%BB%8D%E5%8F%B8%E4%BB%A4%E5%90%8C%E6%97%A5%E9%9B%86%E9%AB%94%E8%BE%AD%E8%81%B7%EF%BC%8C%E5%BC%95%E7%99%BC%E5%9C%8B%E5%85%A7%E6%94%BF%E6%B2%BB%E5%9C%B0%E9%9C%87</link>
